{
  "stem": "9471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I escaped there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there about three months, and I didn't have any money anymore, because I came with a couple hundred, uh, dinar.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That would be maybe $50, you know, I came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a man there, a family who was my, uh, father friend, very well-to-do man.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I came to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I says, Uncle Alfred, can you help me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't have any more money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I cannot pay the rent and the food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He says, oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, I'm going to take the room for you, and you're going to be my mistress.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I heard that, I went home, and I wanted to make suicide.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I didn't succeed, because they find me in time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They pumped my stomach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And three days later, they took us in Italian camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I was the happiest person, because my worry was over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "At least I didn't have worry, how can I pay my rent and the food?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us-- that was in Krvavica in-- in Croatia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Italian put us in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was Italian camp, but no comparison with the other camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They really saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had-- we had barracks, but we had a nice, uh, you know, bath and, uh everything, the food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I met my second husband.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before I met him, I-- I was like loner.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I only played with the children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever I saw the children, I wanted to play with the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was, at the time, a little bit maybe crazy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But then when I met my husband, he was-- first of all, he was very handsome.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was so wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I fell, first time in my life, really, madly in love.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
